data.description: Nice updated property located in Salem.  Updated kitchen and bathrooms with solid surface countertops and flooring.  Nice open floor plan.  Drive around access to back yard for storage and garage.  Mother-in-law apartment underneath garage in back with 2 bedroom, 1 bath, small kitchen and family area.  Property has nice RV parking on the side of the property which includes a rare RV clean out in the driveway.   Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from County records and property appraisal.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
